com.vmware.vcenter.crypto_manager.kms

Interface ProvidersTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Providers
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProvidersStub

    public interface ProvidersTypes
    The Providers interface provides methods to create, retrieve, update, delete, export and import providers. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.2.0.

      static class  ProvidersTypes.Constraints
      The Constraints class contains constraints on a provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.ConstraintsSpec
      The ConstraintsSpec class contains constraints to be imposed on a provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.CreateSpec
      The CreateSpec class contains properties that describe the desired configuration for a new provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.ExportResult
      The ExportResult class contains result of Providers.export(com.vmware.vcenter.crypto_manager.kms.ProvidersTypes.ExportSpec) operation.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.ExportSpec
      The ExportSpec class contains properties that are needed to export a provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.ExportType
      The ExportType enumeration class identifies the type of result that is returned when a provider is exported.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.FilterSpec
      The FilterSpec class contains properties used to filter the results when listing providers.

      The Health enumeration class describes the health status of a provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.ImportResult
      The ImportResult class contains result of the Providers.importProvider(com.vmware.vcenter.crypto_manager.kms.ProvidersTypes.ImportSpec) operation.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.ImportSpec
      The ImportSpec class contains properties that are needed to import a provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.Info
      The Info class contains properties that describe the details of a provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.Location
      The Location class contains the location as well as a token required (as a header in the HTTP GET request) to download the configuration.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.NativeProviderCreateSpec
      The NativeProviderCreateSpec class contains properties that describe the desired configuration for a ProvidersTypes.Type.NATIVE provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.NativeProviderInfo
      The NativeProviderInfo class contains properties that describe details of a native provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.NativeProviderUpdateSpec
      The NativeProviderUpdateSpec class contains properties that describe the desired configuration for ProvidersTypes.Type.NATIVE provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.Summary
      The Summary class contains properties that describe a provider.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.Token
      The Token class contains information about the token required to be passed in the HTTP header in the HTTP GET request to download the provider configuration.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.Type
      The Type enumeration class contains the types of providers.
      static class  ProvidersTypes.UpdateSpec
      The UpdateSpec class contains properties that describe the new configuration for an existing provider.
